{"tid":2113744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反對國安法】Fridays For Freedom 活動 各地民眾連續第三周上載照片撐香港","createTime":"2020-07-18T10:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T14:25:21.000Z","uid":48083,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0402b495879c39ae6bb5dd29a85edd9e2ac75ce9","tid":2113744,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"《港區國安法》引發國際關注，有團體發起「Fridays For Freedom：Free Hong Kong」活動，呼籲各國人士 7 月起逢星期五，在當地中國領事館前手持「Free Hong Kong！」標語拍照，並上載至社交平台。剛過去的周五（17 日），響應行動的人已經連續第三星期，以 #FridaysForFreedom 標籤，上載照片到各個社交網站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-fridays-for-freedom-%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E6%92%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-fridays-for-freedom-%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2580%25B1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BC%2589%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2592%2590%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=2c6dfa53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-fridays-for-freedom-%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2580%25B1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BC%2589%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2592%2590%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&h=9ce793f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-fridays-for-freedo